comments: Aldridge (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ball's (NOP) path.
Favors (NOP) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and disengage with one another during the rebound.
Holiday (NOP) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) while defending him on the perimeter.
Aldridge (SAS) slightly extends his off-arm as he separates from Favors (NOP) on the drive.
Hart (NOP) makes contact with Aldridge's (SAS) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Prior to the inbound, Favors (NOP) and Mills (SAS) make marginal contact with each other during the screen.
Mills (SAS) makes slight contact with Ingram (NOP) on the catch.
White (SAS) makes slight body contact with Ingram (NOP) while defending his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) slightly extends his arm while setting the pick on Ingram (NOP).
Ingram (NOP) legally contest White's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) legally contest Holiday's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Favors (NOP) briefly clamps White's (SAS) arm during the rebound.
